                <br />1 Victoria Street
                <br />London
                <br />SW1H 0ET
                <br />Email: <a href="mailto:dataprotection@beis.gov.uk">dataprotection@beis.gov.uk</a>
            </p>
            
            <h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="updates-to-this-notice">Updates to this notice</h2>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                There may be changes to this privacy notice. Any future change to our privacy policy will only affect how we use any information collected after the date of the change. If you provided information before the change, you will have done so in light of the previous policy statement. We will honour the assurances we gave at the time.                
            </p>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                If this privacy notice changes in any way, we will place an updated version on this page. Regularly reviewing this page ensures you are always aware of what information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances we will share it with other parties. The ‘last updated’ date at the bottom of this page will also change and will include details of the changes made.
            </p>
            <p class="govuk-body">
                If these changes materially affect how your personal data is processed in a way that negatively impacts your data protection rights and/or freedoms, we will take additional steps to let you know, as well as updating this page. For instance, if the changes mean a consent you have previously given us no longer applies, we will contact you to request a new consent and not continue to process your personal data on the basis of the old consent.
            </p>
